data.description: Welcome Home to this like new family home featuring a lot of added extras.  This home features open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, laundry room with sink and cabinets and two-car garage.  The kitchen has been upgraded with new stainless steel appliances, new deep stainless steel kitchen sink, quartz countertops and cabinets have fresh paint.  Nice durable LVP flooring in main rooms and carpet in the bedrooms.  Updated light fixtures throughout this home with cozy tiled gas fireplace in main room.  Spacious laundry room that leads out to large two-car garage.  Back yard is fenced in.  This home is move-in ready for a new family.  Call today for your showing!  Tracy 478-299-4367
